<br>
(well not YET.. lol!!)<br>
<br>
But seriously. Tapping L1 will auto-lock to the nearest enemy. I found it REALLY easy to control the camera by moving close to the enemy I want to attack, tap L1, then commence the attack. After I'm done I target the next one. It's not too hard to get used to (I'm starting to like it).<br>
<br>
The annoying parts are when you are trying to get treasure chests or trying to jump from one place to another... yet your view is partially or completely blocked and you have to jump blindly. That can get pretty frustrating if you wanna get those well hidden secret treasure boxes.  <p><embed src="http://xenoflare.virtualave.net/misc/fluxsig2002.swf" width="170" height="60">
